  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Amtk</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Amtk</application> package contains a basic GTKUIManager
replacement based on GAction.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&amtk-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (FTP): <ulink url="&amtk-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificação MD5: &amtk-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
