        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Espaço em disco estimado exigido: &amtk-buildsize;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tempo de construção estimado: &amtk-time;
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependências de Amtk</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Exigida</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="gtk3"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/> (for documentation) and <xref linkend="valgrind"/>
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">
      Observações de Usuário(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/amtk"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de Amtk</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>Amtk</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir amtk-build &amp;&amp;
cd    amtk-build &amp;&amp;

meson --prefix=/usr --buildtype=release -Dgtk_doc=false .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Para testar os resultados, emita: <command>ninja test</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explicações do Comando</title>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      href="../../xincludes/meson-buildtype-release.xml"/>

    <para>
      <parameter>-Dgtk_doc=false</parameter>: This switch prevents the build
system from generating and installing the API documentation. Omit this
switch if you have <xref linkend="gtk-doc" role="nodep"/> installed and wish
to generate and install the API documentation.
    </para>

  </sect2>

